<td style="text-align:right;font-size:115%;padding-top: 0.6em;">
<div class="noprint plainlinks hlist navbar mini" style="">
<ul>
<li class="nv-view"><a href="Template_Buddhism" title="Template:Buddhism"><span title="View this template" style="">v</span></a></li>
<li class="nv-talk"><a href="Template_talk_Buddhism" title="Template talk:Buddhism"><span title="Discuss this template" style="">t</span></a></li>
<li class="nv-edit"><a class="external text" href="../../w/index-title=Template_Buddhism&action=edit.php.html"><span title="Edit this template" style="">e</span></a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</td>
