<p><a href="Htukkanthein_Temple" title="Htukkanthein Temple">Htukkanthein</a>, one of the most famous temples in <a href="Mrauk_U" title="Mrauk U">Mrauk U</a>, Burma.</p>
</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px">
<div style="width: 155px">
<div class="thumb" style="width: 150px;">
<div style="margin:35px auto;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Wat_Arun_from_Chao_Phraya_River.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bd/Wat_Arun_from_Chao_Phraya_River.jpg/120px-Wat_Arun_from_Chao_Phraya_River.jpg" width="120" height="80" /></a></div>
</div>
<div class="gallerytext">
<p><a href="Wat_Arun" title="Wat Arun">Wat Arun</a> in <a href="Bangkok" title="Bangkok">Bangkok</a>, one of the most famous landmarks in Thailand.</p>
</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px">
<div style="width: 155px">
<div class="thumb" style="width: 150px;">
<div style="margin:30px auto;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Wat_Phra_Chetuphon_Vimolmangklararm_Rajwaramahaviharn_06.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6f/Wat_Phra_Chetuphon_Vimolmangklararm_Rajwaramahaviharn_06.jpg/120px-Wat_Phra_Chetuphon_Vimolmangklararm_Rajwaramahaviharn_06.jpg" width="120" height="90" /></a></div>
</div>
<div class="gallerytext">
<p><a href="Wat_Pho" title="Wat Pho">Wat Pho</a>, one of the largest and oldest temples in Bangkok, Thailand.</p>
</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px">
<div style="width: 155px">
<div class="thumb" style="width: 150px;">
